{"tid":1045581,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《銃夢：戰鬥天使》Alita:Battle Angel 電影討論區 (4)","createTime":"2019-03-03T16:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T16:36:25.000Z","uid":216874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24ee8d5adc349662c90e2ca32535e37440403223","tid":1045581,"uid":216874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"《銃夢：戰鬥天使》Alita:Battle Angel <br />\n<br />\n導演 :羅拔洛迪格斯 <br />\n演員 :基斯杜化華茲 , 珍妮花康納莉 , 馬許沙拉艾利 , 羅莎沙拉撒 <br />\n片長 :2小時2分<br />\n級別 :IIA 級<br />\n語言 :英語 (中文字幕)<br />\n上映 : 5.2.2019 (公映)<br />\n<br />\nIMDB: <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0437086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0437086%2F&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ae3a7fda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0437086/</a><br />\n故事簡介<br />\n幾個世紀後的未來世界裡，合成人艾莉達 (Alita) 躺在Iron City廢鐵區中不省人事，幸得心地善良的機械醫師伊度，將她帶回工作室修理。艾莉達醒來時發現記憶全失，對身處世界一無所知，但一切簇新生活令她充滿好奇，到處探索。伊度極力隱藏艾莉達的神秘過去，而她好友曉高卻試圖勾起她失落記憶，兩人更漸生情愫；同時各方惡勢力逐漸叩上門，危及艾莉達至親，從而啟動她潛藏的逆天戰鬥力！為了解破身世之謎，艾莉達獨力踏上征途，對抗這個黑暗腐朽的世界！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxwHduJUxrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQxwHduJUxrc&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e8a46580\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxwHduJUxrc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxwHduJUxrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQxwHduJUxrc&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e8a46580\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxwHduJUxrc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/r836zrjaxnj21.jpg?width=960&amp;crop=smart&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=7eb1f4a75b4bd28e80ea90363ee15b84b8d705a1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2Fr836zrjaxnj21.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960%26crop%3Dsmart%26auto%3D